<div class="control-panel">
  <div class="accordion">
    <h3 id="accordion-instructions">
      <button type="button" class="accordion-trigger" data-contentid="instructions-content">Instructions</button>
    </h3>
    <div
      class="accordion-content instructions"
      aria-labelledby="accordion-instructions"
      aria-expanded="false"
      id="instructions-content">
      <p>Add as many images as you want using the form below, or create your own from scratch.</p>
      <p>
        You can use any PNG or JPG image from your hard drive, or from a URL.
      </p>
      <h4>Transparent images work best</h4>
      <p>Run your images through
        <a href="https://remove.bg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank">remove.bg</a>
        first.
      </p>
      <h4>Looking for an emoji to start with?</h4>
      <p>Search
        <a href="https://emojipedia.org" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Emojipedia</a>
        and scroll down to the examples for images to save.
      </p>
      <h4>Using the creator</h4>
      <p>Choose bases and accessories from the picker on the left.</p>
      <p>Select images by double-clicking them or click &amp; drag in the canvas. Rotate/flip using the controls.</p>
      <p>Click in blank areas of the canvas to deselect.</p>
      <p>Click "start again" to completely clear the canvas.</p>
      <p>Most of the accessories are colour-customisable - select one and choose the colours from the top panel.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <form class="upload-form accordion" id="form">
    <h3 id="accordion-heading-upload">
      <button type="button" class="accordion-trigger is-open" data-contentid="upload-form">Upload images</button>
    </h3>
    <div
      class="upload-form-content accordion-content is-open"
      id="upload-form"
      aria-expanded="true"
      aria-labelledby="accordion-heading-upload">
      <label for="conditional-reveal-file" class="upload-option">
        <input
          type="radio"
          value="file"
          name="image-upload"
          id="conditional-reveal-file"
          aria-controls="creator-input-file"
          checked>
      </input>
      From file</label>
    <div class="conditional-input" id="conditional-file-input">
      <label for="creator-input-file">Choose an image</label>
      <input name="image" id="creator-input-file" type="file" accept=".jpg, .jpeg, .png"></input>
  </div>
  <label for="conditional-reveal-url" class="upload-option">
    <input type="radio" value="url" name="image-upload" id="conditional-reveal-url" aria-controls="creator-input-url">
  </input>
  From URL</label>
<div class="conditional-input hidden" id="conditional-url-input">
  <label for="creator-input-url">Image URL</label>
  <input name="image-url" id="creator-input-url" type="text"></input></div><p id="image-upload-error" class="upload-error hidden"></p><span>
<button type="submit" id="submit">Upload</button>
